			<li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-wo"><a href="http://wo.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jimbulang_bu_waa-Brëtaañ" title="Jimbulang bu waa-Brëtaañ – Wolof" lang="wo" hreflang="wo">Wolof</a></li>
